candidate_list.title: CTA Digital Xbox 360 - Kinect Perfect Range Anti-Slip Gaming Mat
description: Product Description

The Xbox 360 Kinect is the first of its kind in controller-free motion capture gaming. Make the most of this new technology with the Perfect Range Game Mat for the Xbox 360 Kinect from CTA Digital. The beauty of the Game Mat is that it allows for a clear view of Kinect’s 1 and 2 player gaming zone, while protecting your floors and carpets and reducing noise. By placing the mat centered, 4’ from the Xbox 360 Kinect’s camera, players can see a clear visual guide of the gaming area for a flawless Kinect experience. Without the mat’s visual guide, gamers can easily find themselves outside the gaming zone. While playing a controller-free system it’s also very easy to become misaligned with the camera, making it frustrating to again find the correct area and distance. The Perfect Range Game Mat makes it incredibly easy to stay within Kinect’s gaming zone, but also to find your way back once you’ve moved. It’s also made of durable and comfortable foam, and includes an anti-slip material to keep the mat in place during intense gaming sessions. The Game Mat is compatible with all Xbox 360 Kinect games and rolls up to store easily in your home. The stylish design and practical function of CTA Digital’s Perfect Range Game Mat is sure to make the most of your Xbox 360 Kinect.
